  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/de74e4fea50c3c7fedf0a6bd3b6aeee6.poster.avif?t=1760533200\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/de74e4fea50c3c7fedf0a6bd3b6aeee6.webm?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/de74e4fea50c3c7fedf0a6bd3b6aeee6.mp4?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Glitch Lord has captured our heroes and held them captive in a hellish world in the theme of a 1980’s synth combat arena. You must fight for your survival or you will be shredded into 8-bit guts. Taunt your foes with distraction and acrobatic feats before falling from the sky to deliver swift death.<br><br><i><strong>\"Immerse yourself in a neon-soaked 80s combat arena where every kill is a nod to the retro future we were promised.\"</strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/ddf26a26430f62d0e9e2a9462d10596f.poster.avif?t=1760533200\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/ddf26a26430f62d0e9e2a9462d10596f.webm?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/ddf26a26430f62d0e9e2a9462d10596f.mp4?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Select one of four characters, each with their own style and trash-talking personality.<br></li><li>Taunt, teabag, and spit oral insults at your friends and foes.<br></li><li>Jump and climb anywhere around the arena.<br></li><li>Paint the entire arena with your competitor's blood and guts.<br></li><li>Play offline anytime with the ability to hone your skills against AI bots.<br></li><li>Slay the weak when you prevail; losers at the end of a match get disarmed and nerfed like lambs to the slaughter, allowing the winner to kill with ease.<br></li><li>Awesome 80’s Synthwave Original Soundtrack created just for the game.<br></li><li>Block your foes' directional attacks on the ground, walls, and in the sky, but be warned—they can only take one major hit before needing a quick recharge.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/2a4f93d9820511626a418484418edece.poster.avif?t=1760533200\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/2a4f93d9820511626a418484418edece.webm?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/2a4f93d9820511626a418484418edece.mp4?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/157d1abc9db66fc830913db155fe672d.poster.avif?t=1760533200\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/157d1abc9db66fc830913db155fe672d.webm?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Daggra</i></strong>: She's as cool as a polar bear in a blizzard.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/0ab6d06dfda26301d0a064fc33032f89.poster.avif?t=1760533200\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/0ab6d06dfda26301d0a064fc33032f89.webm?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Toxic Claw</i></strong>: This dude has total attitude and plans on getting you salty.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/cc41de67e948db6ce2fb7da062131c97.poster.avif?t=1760533200\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/cc41de67e948db6ce2fb7da062131c97.webm?t=1760533200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Red Fang</i></strong>: Meditation and honor will bring this warrior victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/aaf680a24772ab23d9ab2a3ff9ea0086.webp?t=1760533200\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751230/extras/aaf680a24772ab23d9ab2a3ff9ea0086.poster.avif?t=1760533200\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=160 /></picture></span><br><strong><i>Charm Caster</i></strong>: She is flirty and fun, manipulating and distracting opponents.",
